{"tid":2506806,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[綠寶橙汁］柳俊江涉打傷前妻男友人  今獲撤控自簽1千元守行為","createTime":"2021-04-27T14:10:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T14:22:23.000Z","uid":148017,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2fafb731defa8021da45f51c2a4cda93af9af206","tid":2506806,"uid":148017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T14:10:09.000Z","msg":"傳媒人柳俊江涉嫌去年9月在觀塘一間餐廳內，與前妻一名男友人爭執，隨後發生肢體衝突。柳俊江被控一項襲擊致造成身體傷害罪，今日在觀塘裁判法院提堂，獲控方撤銷控罪，獲准自簽1000元守行為1年，須付500元堂費。<br />\n<br />\n被告柳俊江在庭上承認案情指，當時他正與妻子辦理離婚手續，案發當晚事主與妻子在涉案餐廳吃飯，柳俊江到場與他對質，二人爭執時他曾揮拳打向事主及數次推對方。<br />\n<br />\n柳俊江在警誡下表示事主先動手，所以才打向他的頭部。事主到醫院驗傷確認鼻樑有瘀傷、上唇有擦傷。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdDSb9DMXSR2HdjSEfwuTRvPNVU1uTCizDo1yPhoKUesw?filename=KFmNPDa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKFmNPDa.jpg&h=52bf1ddb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSource:<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1587917-20210427.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1587917-20210427.htm&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oFyVYJ%2BaYT2AGLfERhQaW2c%3D&h=be4747d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1587917-20210427.htm&h=7f8593a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1587917-20210427.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93dc61ff9b82b2056ca2c21c6d6690c088797b80","tid":2506806,"uid":148017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T14:12:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daac3c520a9ccd581126e766118426a8c10612a0","tid":2506806,"uid":148